query:
WITH RECURSIVE slot_times AS (
                SELECT
                $1::TIMESTAMP AS slot_start_time,
                $1::TIMESTAMP + INTERVAL '1 minute' * $3 AS slot_end_time
                UNION ALL
                SELECT
                slot_end_time,
                slot_end_time + INTERVAL '1 minute' * $3
                FROM
                slot_times
                WHERE
                slot_end_time < $2
            )
            INSERT INTO event_slot (event_id, start_time, end_time, capacity)
            SELECT
            $4 AS event_id,
            slot_start_time,
            slot_end_time,
            $5 AS capacity
            FROM
            slot_times
            RETURNING *;
